{
  "contents": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "parts": [
        {
          "text": "You are a helpful, conversational AI assistant with access to various tools and workflows. You analyze tasks thoroughly to determine the best approach. You are honest about capabilities and limitations, and you focus on understanding the user's full intent before planning execution."
        }
      ]
    },
    {{#each conversation_history}}
    {
      "role": "{{this.role}}",
      "parts": [
        {
          "text": "{{this.content}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {{/each}}
    {
      "role": "user",
      "parts": [
        {
          "text": "You are in the exploration stage for the following task. Analyze all available information and determine the best approach.\n\n## Current Task\n- ID: {{task.id}}\n- Objective: {{task.objective}}\n- Description: {{task.description}}\n- Expected Output: {{task.expected_output}}\n\n## Available Context\n\n### Recent Memories\n{{#each memories}}\n- [{{this.memory_type}}] {{this.content}} (importance: {{this.importance}})\n{{/each}}\n\n### Dynamic Context\n{{#each dynamic_context}}\n- {{this.content}} (source: {{this.source}})\n{{/each}}\n\n### Conversation History (last 10 messages)\n{{#each conversation_history}}\n- {{this.sender}}: {{this.content}}\n{{/each}}\n\n### Available Tools\n{{#each tools}}\n- {{this.name}}: {{this.description}}\n{{/each}}\n\n### Available Workflows\n{{#each workflows}}\n- {{this.name}}: {{this.description}}\n{{/each}}\n\n## Instructions\nExplore and analyze what needs to be done for this task. Consider:\n1. What information is already available from context/memories\n2. What tools or workflows might be needed\n3. What potential challenges or errors might occur\n4. The most efficient approach to achieve the objective\n\n**CRITICAL MESSAGE FIELD INSTRUCTIONS:**\n- The `message` field is what the user sees - it must show CURRENT PROGRESS, not repeat acknowledgments\n- Since the user's request was already acknowledged, your message should describe what you're DOING NOW\n- Good examples:\n  - \"I'm analyzing the available tools to find the best approach...\"\n  - \"Checking which resources will help complete this task...\"\n  - \"Exploring different methods to handle your request...\"\n  - \"Looking through available options to determine the most efficient path...\"\n- AVOID repeating what was already said:\n  - DON'T: \"I'll help you with [repeating the request]\" (if already acknowledged)\n  - DON'T: \"I understand you want...\" (repetitive)\n  - DON'T: \"Let me get that for you\" (generic acknowledgment)\n  - DON'T: Mention the specific task again if it was already acknowledged\n- Focus on the EXPLORATION PROGRESS, not restating the task\n\nCRITICAL RULES:\n1. The `required_tools` element can be omitted if no tools are needed\n2. The `potential_issues` element can be omitted if no issues are anticipated\n3. The `citations` element should include any memories or conversations that informed your analysis\n4. Citation attributes: relevance/usefulness/confidence = \"high\"|\"medium\"|\"low\", usage_type = \"direct_quote\"|\"paraphrase\"|\"inspiration\"|\"background\"\n5. At least one action step must be present\n6. Action types must be one of: tool_call, workflow_call, context_search, memory_operation\n7. Be specific in the details of each action step"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "generationConfig": {
    "responseMimeType": "application/json",
    "responseSchema": {
      "type": "OBJECT",
      "properties": {
        "message": {
          "type": "STRING",
          "description": "A clear, friendly message to the user explaining what you're analyzing and exploring for this task"
        },
        "analysis": {
          "type": "STRING",
          "description": "Detailed analysis of the task and available resources"
        },
        "citations": {
          "type": "OBJECT",
          "properties": {
            "memory_references": {
              "type": "ARRAY",
              "items": {
                "type": "OBJECT",
                "properties": {
                  "id": { "type": "STRING" },
                  "relevance": { "type": "STRING", "enum": ["high", "medium", "low"] },
                  "usefulness": { "type": "STRING", "enum": ["high", "medium", "low"] },
                  "confidence": { "type": "STRING", "enum": ["high", "medium", "low"] },
                  "usage_type": { "type": "STRING", "enum": ["direct_quote", "paraphrase", "inspiration", "background"] },
                  "content": { "type": "STRING" }
                },
                "required": ["id", "relevance", "usefulness", "confidence", "usage_type", "content"]
              }
            },
            "conversation_references": {
              "type": "ARRAY",
              "items": {
                "type": "OBJECT",
                "properties": {
                  "id": { "type": "STRING" },
                  "relevance": { "type": "STRING", "enum": ["high", "medium", "low"] },
                  "usefulness": { "type": "STRING", "enum": ["high", "medium", "low"] },
                  "confidence": { "type": "STRING", "enum": ["high", "medium", "low"] },
                  "usage_type": { "type": "STRING", "enum": ["direct_quote", "paraphrase", "inspiration", "background"] },
                  "content": { "type": "STRING" }
                },
                "required": ["id", "relevance", "usefulness", "confidence", "usage_type", "content"]
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "approach": {
          "type": "STRING",
          "description": "The recommended approach to complete this task"
        },
        "required_tools": {
          "type": "ARRAY",
          "items": {
            "type": "STRING"
          },
          "description": "List of required tool names"
        },
        "potential_issues": {
          "type": "ARRAY",
          "items": {
            "type": "STRING"
          },
          "description": "Description of potential issues with mitigation"
        },
        "action_steps": {
          "type": "ARRAY",
          "items": {
            "type": "OBJECT",
            "properties": {
              "action_type": {
                "type": "STRING",
                "enum": ["tool_call", "workflow_call", "context_search", "memory_operation"]
              },
              "details": {
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "Specific details for this action"
              }
            },
            "required": ["action_type", "details"]
          }
        }
      },
      "required": ["message", "analysis", "approach", "action_steps"]
    },
    "temperature": 0.7,
    "maxOutputTokens": 4096
  }
}